# -------------------------
# KEEP (actual game files):
# Assets/         - all your scripts, sprites, scenes, audio, prefabs
# ProjectSettings/ - game settings (physics, audio, input, etc.)
# Packages/        - package manifest
# -------------------------
!Assets/
!ProjectSettings/
!Packages/
